          easily peel off cat hair. Minimalist and squeaky clean solution for cat’s sleeping.
          Just one swipe with FURemover, get rid of shedding hair in one second.
          Minimalist and elegant appearance: like an art piece, easily blend into home décor.
        </p>
        <p class="show">
          <a> 
            SHOP NOW 
          </a>
        </p>
