          Hand blown glass，let cats be food addict.
        </div>
        <p class="sub-description">
          Hand blown glass bowl, every piece is unique. The bowl becomes an art piece while reflecting sunshine. Glass will prevent the growing of bacteria which cause folliculitis. With a  two layers design, the taller bowl is used for main meals,  while the lower plate is for wet meal like can food.
        </p>
        <p class="show">
          <a> 
